               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Photographs include two photo postcards of Raymong and Marcelle Deghels, and one news agency photograph of a man appearing to be Deghels being removed from a plane on a stretcher. Personal effects include a graduation certificate, marriage certificate, and documents related to his service in World War I.</p>
